    skos:scopeNote "Primarily relevant for US-based institutions. Nordic museums should generally use Public Domain Mark or country-specific assessments instead."@en ;
    dcterms:source <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/> .

# ── 19/55: Copyright Not Evaluated ──
