    skos:definition "The most restrictive tier in the Europeana licensing framework. Includes InC (In Copyright) and CC-BY-NC-ND. Content is viewable on Europeana but not reusable."@en ;
    mhub:category "europeana-framework" ;
    skos:broader nr:europeana-framework ;
    skos:scopeNote "Content at this tier has limited visibility and reuse potential on Europeana. Aim for more open tiers when possible to maximize cultural impact."@en ;
    dcterms:source <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/> .

